Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean looks so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dizelmine! I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could take you \Nthere too, Yuriyuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. Today, I have an \Nimportant meeting to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go for a visit some other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's no fun. Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You might get sick again \Nif you overexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{You should be taking a break after our long journey.}You should take this time to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:01:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize this is part of your duties,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still must applaud you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Assign more chaperons to her\Nso that she doesn't go off on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pass on your instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on ya.
