Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that thing \Nfrom yesterday was all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean about the experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There was that \Nthing with Midori
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and the girl who appeared \Nin my cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What was she trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He would never forgive \Nme for seeking asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm sure Asteria will make things work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't joke about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Watabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I will begin \Npreparations right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've received word that \Nshuttles have departed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}both the Le Garite and De Metrio \Nmother ships with their respective kings aboard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this ends \Nwithout any incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if a fist fight breaks out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's better than having them \Nstart a galactic war near Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to see you're in good health too, Captain Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,More lady troubles I see, \Nby the looks of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty, King of Le Garite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you install this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm here with friends. \NHow about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here with my subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Regal, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed \Nat all, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears the information \Nwe have of the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,being best friends since \Nyour Academy days is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We've prepared a quiet location \Nsuited for your historical conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my younger sister \Naboard this vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She and her two friends \Nare engaging in girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say? First one to find \Nthem can revoke their asylum status?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like becoming the king has \Ngiven you a better sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're starting this already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Asteria, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's showtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,On my cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the quiet place suited \Nfor our historic conference, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you put her up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that girl's the \Ntype who listens to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to hear what \Nthe boys have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About our childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But come to think of it, weren't we locked up together like this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when our shuttle reactor went into overload after failing on a subspace trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the year I went to study abroad at your Academy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We were both in our first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've just waited for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but thanks to your meddling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it took them two \Nmore weeks to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Except if I hadn't, the ship \Nwould've been completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was alone, \NI could have saved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So they both went \Nto the same school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder they seem to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look that way to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, looks like we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Moid?! And... why're you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we'd like to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Villagiulio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the middle of a conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that a conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I made these special arrangements for those two shy boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing you say will change \Nthe Chairman's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just watch and \Nsee how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, wasn't yesterday the first time \Nyou witnessed the power of the Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you used your sister for an experiment,\NI hear you were unable to open the Rin-ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought the legend might've scared you and kept you awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother was also scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a scaredy-cat, \Njust like you, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, \NI didn't get any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With that power, I can \Nsolve the 1,000-year problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the rumors about you wanting to \Nuse the Vox to destroy our planet are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish to avert the disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You, more than anyone, should know the danger of the Vox.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Under our research and care,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we can expand on \NVox Aura's potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can avoid further tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Aura's pilot is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... {\i1}special?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's finally \Nrevealing his true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really that into Madoka,\Nthen I may need to change plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell, why don't we just fight over her as warring nations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An unregistered aircraft has \Nleft the Le Garite mother ship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and is headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim?{he's dead}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No response from the \NOccupation Forces, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're letting it through. \NGet me through to Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadokoro here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From Le Garite?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,An Ovid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to explain, Moid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some pretty bad flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of your pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No complaints if we \Ntake care of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest. Go easy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That pilot sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I'm any better, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That direction! \NIt's headed for Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a Kamopaccio, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. One Kamopaccio \Ncoming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Izo! It's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You worried about that \Nthing from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If what happened on \NMilitia happens on this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,think how many people would die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The king of Le Garite and Villagiulio\Nare in talks to avoid just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano paved the way for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How many more of these \NSangayaki Lunch Specials do we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Three more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An Ovid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A Le Garite production model!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap, I think \Nit's coming right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You look busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. Gotta get to Kamogawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll talk to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is \NLe Garite thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suppose they're \Nhere for the conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, they're nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Le Garite pilot! \NYou can hear me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kamogawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a designated neutral zone \Nof De Metrio and Le Garite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow... I hurt my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your hands off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to speak with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! Array!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you recognize me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Lord Dizelmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke your promise \Nand came here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a bad girl, Yuriyuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriyuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess of De Metrio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Villagiulio's \Nreal younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I know that in his heart, he considers you as his little sister, Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry about which \Nof you two he loves more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Lan. That's not \Nthe problem right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. His real sister, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lan, what was Yurikano \Ndoing on Le Garite?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you come \Non the same ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Lady Yurikano several \Ntimes when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never saw her on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know that \Nwe were on board together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother didn't say \Nanything during our trip here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It means your \Nyounger sister is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking why she \Nwas with the Le Garite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I rescued her from the \NTragedy of Militia Zodia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,While you were busy leading some rogues and calling yourselves Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For a while, I feared \Nshe wouldn't make it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but {we finally managed to heal her up to this point.}she finally managed \Nto recover as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As her older brother, \Nshouldn't you be happy for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This man is your real older brother, Yuriyuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't remember a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not even about her being the princess of De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Villagiulio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Biotelemetry numbers are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Her DNA pattern is a perfect match with Lady Yurikano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's behaving exactly like \Nwhen she was a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right down to calling \Nherself Yuriyuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to \Ntry to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving without \NLord Dizelmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've trained her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, \Nwhat about our conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it was our fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think continuing the \Ntalks might be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall meet at the \NIntergalactic Conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse us, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Villagiulio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to \Nlet them go like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't talk to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Muginami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But! But I feel so \Nsorry for Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to \Napologize for, Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go and see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We should act now while \Nit's still fresh in our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask you one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was all this commotion \Npart of your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak \Nwith Miss Yurikano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you appeared \Nin my cockpit, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cockpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind telling me what this is about, Miss Kyouno Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, during the \Ncourse of our experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,she appeared in \Nthe cockpit of Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very odd. She was \Nwith me the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was definitely \NMiss Yurikano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yuriyuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recall meeting \Nwith Miss Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You... are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know you. {lol this was a nice troll}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after you grappled \Nand tussled me like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! What about before that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We also met another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Asteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough. \NNow's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I guess \Nwe'll do as she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's definitely \Nthat girl. I'm positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she's the \Nreal Miss Yurikano,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't she act \Nmore unwilling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we need to \Nhave a proper talk with her!{realtalk}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, Big Brother \NGiuvi and Lan's brother will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's sneak in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak in where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stay here, you'll \Nnever get a chance to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Yurikano is on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We will continue negotiations \Nregarding Lady Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Moid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to assign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,more chaperons to \NYurikano, did I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, it {\i1}did {\i0}allow us to gather some unexpected information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to \N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}return to Le Garite...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,with, uh... my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,'Scuse us, coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Never been to Tokyo, but \Nouter space just fascinates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been begging Laffy \N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}to take me there with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can call me Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And this here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki Namie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.31,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right to let them go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! We're in a big hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's no excuse for me \Nto manhandle my fishnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To a fisherman, they're \Nnearly as dear as life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys should know that by now \Nafter being in Kamogawa for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So Izo, when are you going to ask Sachi out to the movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I never made such a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! How tangled \Ncan these nets get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The Le Garite \Nshuttle's taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! How freakin' awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}this{\i0} is outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Success says, "Wow"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just leave it to me", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Super amazing. yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"After all, I'm a member of Kiss", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is crazy, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Super amazing, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun?! I feel sorry for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take off \Nthose disguises now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Madoka. Miss Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Dizelmine is hellbent on going to war with me.
