Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! This spaceship is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are even sections of it that I'm not familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's where \NMiss Yurikano is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, she wouldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, that place is an eel farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This spaceship really is huge...
